11/07/2005
BEIJING, China -- Deputy Greek Culture Minister Fani Pali Petralia visited China on Sunday (10 July) and said Athens could transfer some of its experience and know-how in organising the 2004 Summer Olympics to Beijing.
She noted that such co-operation could broaden bilateral co-operation in other areas.
Beijing is hosting the 2008 Games.
(ANA - 10/07/05)
